Ridgewood , N . J . , utility seeks rate hike - paper . Ridgewood , N . J . ' s water utility , which also serves Midland Park , Glen Rock , and Wyckoff , is seeking a 26 percent rate increase , the Bergen Record reported Tuesday . The utility plans to ask the state ' s Local Finance Board to approve the higher rate , and does not foresee additional increases before 2001 . If approved , the increase would be to $ 2 . 29 per 1 , 000 gallons from $ 1 . 82 . Utility officials attributed the need for a rate increase to the costs associated with past capital projects . - - U . S . Municipal Desk , 212 - 859 - 1650 
